guna.name: Varna
guna.description: Varna represents the working attitude and capacity.  The  bridegroom's capacity needs to be higher than that of the bride for smooth running of the family. The boy and the girl both belong to Shudra Varna. This type of combination is very much favorable for a union. For this couple Varna Koot is Good.

guna.name: Vasya
guna.description: Vasya was used to determine whether there will be a dedicated and compatible relationship between two people. The boy and the girl both belong to Manava Vasya. This is excellent match. For this couple Vasya Koot is Excellent.

guna.name: Tara
guna.description: Tara is used to calculate the health and well-being of the bride and groom after marriage. The boy and the girl both belong to same Tara Group. The boy's nakshatra Purva Bhadrapada is 0 th position from girl's nakshatra Purva Bhadrapada and this is Benefic. At the same time The girl's nakshatra Purva Bhadrapada is  0 th position from boy's nakshatra Purva Bhadrapada and this is Benefic This is so far the best compatible match. For this couple Tara Koot is Excellent.

guna.name: Yoni
guna.description: Yoni indicates the physical and sexual compatibility between a couple. The boy and the girl both belong to same Yoni Singha This is a warm and gratifying combination. For this couple Yoni Koot is Excellent.

guna.name: Graha Maitri
guna.description: Graha Maitri is used to examine the strength of the love between the couple. This is achieved by comparing the sign lords of the moon in the chart of the bride and groom. The boy and the girl both belong to same Rasi Lord Saturn. The boy and the girl both comes under the same Rasi Kumbha. This is one of the best compatible match. For this couple Graha Maitri Koot is Excellent.

guna.name: Gana
guna.description: Gana is used to identify an individuals temperament. The boy and the girl both belong to same Gana Manushya. This is considered to be an excellent combination for gana match. For this couple Gana Koot is Excellent.

guna.name: Bhakoot
guna.description: Bhakoot or Rashikoot testing is used to verify the overall health, welfare and prosperity of a family after marriage. It is believed that Bhakoot Dosha can affect the intimacy between the couple and cause delays in pregnancy. Zodiac sign for of the boy and the girl is Kumbha. This is an excellent combination from the happiness and prosperity point of view. For this couple Bhakoot Koot is Excellent.

guna.name: Nadi
guna.description: Nadi testing is to check the genetic compatibility of the bride and groom to ensure they are capable of producing healthy children. Nadi Koot is given supreme priority during match making. The boy and the girl both belong to same Nadi Adi. This is inauspicious combination. For this couple Nadi Koot is not Good.

exceptions: Gun Milan Shows Nadi Maha Dosha But dosha loses its maleficence because bride and bridegroom have the same rasi lord.

schema.description: Object representing success response for detailed Porutham check API query.

matches.name: Dina Porutham
matches.description: The availability of dina porutham in the charting denotes good health and prosperity for both the husband and the wife with freedom from poverty, sicknesses and disease; the two are therefore expected to enjoy all comforts in a long and a happy married life. Boy's nakshatra Shravana is in 8th position from girl's nakshatra Swati. For this couple Dina Porutham is Good.

matches.name: Gana Porutham
matches.description: Gana porutham takes into account the matching of the nature of both the boy and the girl to assure compatibility of mind, body and sensuality after marriage. The girl belongs to Deva gana and boy belongs to Deva gana. For this couple Gana Porutham is Good.

matches.name: Mahendra Porutham
matches.description: Mahendra Porutham is considered for the longevity, wealth and progeny. According to this, the family will have children and prosperity. Also, the husband will have the capability of protecting his wife and their children from evil of the world and provide for them in kind and in finances. Boy's Nakshatra Shravana is in 8th position from girl's nakshatra Swati. For this couple Mahendra Porutham is Not Satisfactory.

matches.name: Stree Deergha Porutham
matches.description: Stree deergha porutham ensures the female counterpart's well being, longevity and prosperity. Boy's Nakshatra Shravana counted from Girl's nakshatra Swati is above 7th position. For this couple Stree Deergha Porutham is Satisfactory.

matches.name: Yoni Porutham
matches.description: Yoni Porutham is important because this is the porutham which helps in determining the sexual compatibility between the couple after marriage. Boy's Nakshatra belongs to Female Constellation and Girl's nakshatra belongs to Male Constellation. Boy's Yoni and Girl's are not enemies. So it will turn out to be a happy one. For this couple Yoni Porutham is Satisfactory.

matches.name: Veda Porutham
matches.description: The Vedha Porutham talks about the feasibility or possibility of the couples living together. That is, the perfect Vedha Porutham assures that the couples live together and do not get separated under any circumstances. Boy's nakshatra and Girl's nakshatra have no affliction. So there is veda porutham. For this couple Veda Porutham is Good.

matches.name: Rajju Porutham
matches.description: Rajju porutham is said to be the most important porutham, as it denotes longevity of the boy in the married life. Boy's Nakshatra Shravana and girls Nakshatra Swati is in the Kanta rajju.  For this couple Rajju Porutham is Not Satisfactory.

matches.name: Rasi Porutham
matches.description: Rasi Porutham is well known to represent compatibility of the birth stars or the zodiac signs of the couple. Prosperous life is said to belong to those whose Rasi porutham is found compatible. Boy's rasi is Makara and Girl's rasi is Tula. Boy's rasi  Makara is in 4th position from Girl's rasi Tula, there will be poverty and struggle. For this couple Rasi Porutham is Not Satisfactory.

matches.name: Rasyadhipa Porutham
matches.description: Rasyadhipa Porutham refers to the birth stars of both the girl and the boy with their lords who should be in friendship with each other for a compatible marriage.  If the lords of the birth stars of the boy are in friendship with the lords of the birth stars of the girl the marriage will be a happy and a longlasting one. Boys rasyadhipan is Saturn and girls rasyadhipan is Venus. Saturn and Venus are Friends. For this couple Rasyadhipa Porutham is Good.

matches.name: Vasya Porutham
matches.description: Vasya porutham denotes compatibility between the zodiac signs of the couple that is to get married. Therefore, if there is agreement between their kootas, this enables mutual love and affection to be enhanced and to continue between the man and the wife. Boy's rasi is Makara and Girl's rasi is Tula. Here Girls's rasi is the vasya rasi of Boys rasi. For this couple Vasya Porutham is Good.

Parameter `planets` is optional and by default the api returns all planets excluding `URANUS`, `NEPTUNE` and `PLUTO`.

List of Planets and their ID's

|Planet Name|Planet ID|
|---|---|
|SUN|0|
|MOON|1|
|MERCURY|2|
|VENUS|3|
|MARS|4|
|JUPITER|5|
|SATURN|6|
|URANUS|7|
|NEPTUNE|8|
|PLUTO|9|
|ASCENDANT|100|
|RAHU|101|
|KETU|102|

remedies: It is considered that if a manglik person marries to another manglik person then the manglik dosha gets cancelled and has no effect.
Worship Lord Hanuman by reciting Hanuman Chalisa daily & visit the temple of Lord Hanuman on Tuesdays.
The ill effects of Manglik Dosha can be cancelled by performing a "Kumbh Vivah" in which the manglik marries a banana tree, a peepal tree, or a statue of God Vishnu before the actual wedding.
The ill effects of Manglik Dosha can be reduced with the application of Special Pooja, Mantras, Gemstones and Charities.
Donate blood on a Tuesday in every three months, if health permits.
Worship banyan tree with milk mixed with something sweet.
Start a fast in a rising moon period on a Tuesday.

yoga_list.name: Raja Yoga
yoga_list.description: A typical Raja Yoga happens when two or more than two planets (out of which atleast one should be the lord of 'Kendra' & the other should be the lord of 'Trikon') is in a relationship with each other. This relationship can be a combination, bidirectional vision or exchange of zodiacs. A person with a Raja Yoga enjoys social status and fame.  Recognition and laurels will follow them for their efforts on various matters. In this chart there is relationship between Mercury, Venus, Jupiter & Saturn planets.

yoga_list.name: Malavya Yoga
yoga_list.description: The Malavya yoga, being one of the five of Panchmaha Purusha Yoga is a really auspicious yoga. Malvaya Yoga is formed when Venus is in its own sign (Taurus or Libra) or in exaltation (Pisces) and occupies a Kendra house from the Ascendant or from Moon. A strong Venus that occupies a powerful position in the chart will yield more positive benefits of this yoga.  Individuals born with Malavya yoga appreciate the value of all things in their life. So they never take things for granted and enjoy even the seemingly unimportant things in life. In this chart Venus is in its own sign.

yoga_list.name: Sasa Yoga
yoga_list.description: Sasa Yoga, being one of the five of Panchmaha Purusha Yoga is a really auspicious yoga. When Saturn is in its own sign (Capricorn or Aquarius) or in its exaltation sign (Libra) and occupies Kendra house either from Ascendant or from Moon, a Sasa yoga is the result. The native of Sasa yoga loves travelling and is very appreciative of beauty and nature. They are noble and humble in all their endeavours. They are known to do well in politics. In this chart Saturn is in its own sign.

yoga_list.name: Sunafa Yoga
yoga_list.description: If any planet other than the sun occupies the second house from moon sign then such a birth chart has the Sunafa yoga. This yoga is known to bring, good fortune and wealth. Generally such individuals are quite natured and they enjoy activities like music and poetry. In this chart planets Mars & Ascendant are in the 2nd house from Moon.

yoga_list.name: Anafa Yoga
yoga_list.description: Anafa Yoga is as a result of a benefice planet (except Sun, Rahu and Ketu) in the twelfth house from Moon. The native of Anafa yoga enjoys good health. They will be able to get people on their side with their charm and wit. They will be a master in communication and  may also be interest in humanitarian causes and charitable acts. In this chart planets Jupiter & Saturn are in the 12th house from Moon.

yoga_list.name: Durudhara Yoga
yoga_list.description: Durudhara Yoga is formed as a result of planets (except Sun, Rahu and Ketu) being on either side of Moon. Those with Durudhara Yoga are blessed with many luxuries in life. They are known to enjoy theses  comforts of life, but they will be generous and charitable too. In this chart planets Mars, Jupiter & Saturn are on either side of Moon.

yoga_list.name: Kemadruma Yoga
yoga_list.description:
Kemadruma Yoga is formed when the second and twelfth house from the moon is not occupied by any planet (except Sun, Rahu and Ketu). This leaves either side of Moon empty, making it weak.  Struggles and Poverty is typical of a person born with Kemadruma Yoga.  Being away from family and loved ones is also seen in such natives.
                Some remedies that are advised to minimise the negative effects of Kemadruma yoga is:
                Fasting on Purnima days for four consecutive years is known to minimise the negative effects of Kemadruma yoga. You may begin this fast starting from a Purnima that happens on a Monday or even from the day of Chitra nakshatra whenever it falls on a Monday.
                Pay a visit  to Siva's temple on Mondays and perform abhisheka using cow’s milk on Shivalinga
                Worshipping Lord Shiva and goddess Parvati is advised.
                Reciting the Shivapanchakshari mantra ‘Om Namah Shivaya’ with a Rudraksha mala is also specially helpful.
                Reading the Sri Sukta regularly and keeping a Dakshinavarti shell in the house is also helpful. Fill water in the  Dakshinavarti shell and puse this water to perform abhisheka on the idol of of Goddess Lakshmi.
                Wearing a Sri Yantra set in silver with a pearl is also especially helpful for Kemadruma natives.

yoga_list.name: Veshi Yoga
yoga_list.description: Your kundli does not have veshi yoga.

yoga_list.name: Vaasi Yoga
yoga_list.description: Vashi yoga is found in a birth chart when any planet except Rahu, Ketu and Moon is placed in the twelfth house from the Sun. Wealth, luxury and joy are seen to follow those with this yoga. Those with Vaasi yoga have a likeable personality and are talented, intelligent, systematic and diligent in anything that they undertake. They are honest and true to their words at all times. In this chart planets Mercury & Venus are in the 12th house from Sun.

yoga_list.name: Daridra Yoga

yoga_list.name: Grahan Yoga
yoga_list.description: One of the most inauspicious yogas in astrology is Grahan Yoga. This occurs when either the Sun or Moon is with either the Rahu or Ketu in a birth chart. Depending on the houses impacted in Grahan Yoga, various spheres of life are impacted. Promises are seldom kept and trying to find an escape route to run away from their responsibilities becomes a part and parcel of the native's life. In this chart Sun is in Ketu.

yoga_list.name: Shakat Yoga

yoga_list.name: Kuja Yoga
yoga_list.description: The Kuja Yoga also known as Mangal Dosa or Mangalik Dosa is formed when Mars is in the 1st, 4th, 7th, 8th and 12th house of a chart. Some remedies to appease the Mars god are: When two people with Kuja Dosha enter a married life, the negative effects are cancelled. Chanting Navgraha mantra is helpful. Meditating and chanting on Gayatri Mantra and Hanuman Chalisa is particularly helpful. Worshipping Hanuman and visiting a Hanuman temple on Tuesdays is helpful. Observing a fast on Tuesdays is also helpful. In this chart Mars is in Kendra.

yoga_list.name: Kemdrum Yoga
